        "scenario": "Backfill overwrites a preference that was just updated via dual-write",
        "handling": "unhandled",
        "recommendation": "MUST-HAVE: Backfill should use INSERT INTO user_preferences ... ON CONFLICT (user_id) DO NOTHING, or compare updated_at timestamps. Never blindly overwrite rows that may have been dual-written with fresher data."
