        "recommendation": "MUST-HAVE: Add a feature flag (e.g., READ_FROM_NEW_TABLE=true) so all instances switch reads atomically via config, not deployment. This decouples the code deploy from the behavior change. Alternatively, implement fallback: if user_preferences row is missing, fall back to users.preferences_json and log a warning."
